{"tid":2199250,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★ 北角檢測中心 十分鐘內只有一人到場採樣","createTime":"2020-09-12T05:10:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T08:09:04.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"bdcc48b002b5108404dad86060e83a2b840d6b94","tid":2199250,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T05:10:28.000Z","msg":"Now新聞台】普及社區檢測計劃57間檢測中心今天起再延長服務三天，截至上午八時半，累計有162萬5千人接受採樣。<br />\n<br />\n在其中一間檢測中心秀茂坪社區會堂，有市民來到接受採樣，進入前職員為他們量度體溫。秀茂坪社區會堂在計劃展開最初幾天曾經爆滿，屬57間延長服務的檢測中心之一。<br />\n<br />\n在另一間檢測中心北角官立小學，來接受採樣的人明顯較少，早上曾經在十分鐘內只有一人到場採樣。<br />\n<br />\n公務員事務局局長聶德權在社交網站表示，截至上午八時半，累計有162萬5千人接受採樣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5dDcjwK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5dDcjwK.png&h=15bfbe7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=405296\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D405296&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9f4HZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=cac32549\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D405296&h=a86b8883\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=405296</a>"},{"pid":"58366cc8bcb3dad1ba74ec135a7f48d016a88aaf","tid":2199250,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T05:10:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe2e71c8c424e5e449a8ad37d695fdceaa4cfe4a","tid":2199250,"uid":209024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"re